Copenhagen comorbidity in HIV infection (COCOMO) study: a study protocol for a 
longitudinal, non-interventional assessment of non-AIDS comorbidity in HIV 
infection in Denmark.

Ronit A(1), Haissman J(1), Kirkegaard-Klitbo DM(1)(2), Kristensen TS(3), Lebech 
AM(2), Benfield T(2), Gerstoft J(1), Ullum H(4), Køber L(5), Kjær A(6), Kofoed 
